gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Celtics 132, Wizards 122
gameRecap.excerpt: The Celtics defeated the Wizards, 132-122. Payton Pritchard put up a career-high 38 points, along with nine rebounds and 12 assists for the Celtics, while Svi Mykhailiuk added 26 points (6-8 3PT FG), five rebounds and five assists in the victory. Eugene Omoruyi tallied a career-high 26 points (4-6 3PT FG) for the Wizards in the losing effort. The Celtics finish the regular season at 64-18, while the Wizards finish 15-67.
